OL,3,CMeet Hugo the underwater hoover
OL,4,Ckeeping a Guernsey harbour spotless
OL,6,FAn underwater hoover designed to clean
OL,7,Fup a Guernsey harbour has been
OL,8,Flaunched.
OL,10,FHugo the 'harbour hoover' is a device
OL,11,Fknown as a portbin and has been
OL,12,Fintroduced to remove rubbish and
OL,13,Fdebris from Victoria Marina in St
OL,14,FPeter Port.
OL,16,FIt is emptied everyday and every cycle
OL,17,Fcan remove up to five litres of
OL,18,Frubbish from the water.
