OL,3,CMeet Hugo the underwater hoover
OL,4,Ckeeping a Guernsey harbour spotless
OL,6,F"In an ideal world we wouldn't have
OL,7,Fsingle-use plastics and we wouldn't
OL,8,Fneed devices like this but it's good
OL,9,Fwe can contribute to purchase things
OL,10,Flike this to really make a difference."
OL,12,FMike Harris, Guernsey's Assistant
OL,13,FHarbour Master, added that the hoover
OL,14,Fcould revolutionise the way the marina
OL,15,Fis cleaned.
OL,17,FMr Harris said: "It's on all the time.
OL,18,FSo unlike our staff who go out once or
OL,19,Ftwice a day who go out and do what's
OL,20,Fcalled the 'gashing' and, like I say,
OL,21,Fthe more we get, the better."
