OL,3,CMeet Hugo the underwater hoover
OL,4,Ckeeping a Guernsey harbour spotless
OL,6,FMr Harris told ITV News he also hopes
OL,7,Fthe hoover can continue working in the
OL,8,Fwinter months, even as colder and
OL,9,Fpotentially more extreme weather takes
OL,10,Fhold.
OL,12,FThe Rotary Guernesiais held a
OL,13,Fcompetition to name the hoover.
OL,15,FHugo was chosen after eight-year-old
OL,16,FOlivia suggested naming the machine
OL,17,Fafter famous novelist, poet and
OL,18,Fdramatist Victor Hugo.
