OL,6,FCorey Boyd, Olivia's dad, said his
OL,7,Fdaughter loved the fact that the
OL,8,Fhoover was named Hugo.
OL,10,FHe said: "She started jumping around
OL,11,Fand even came to see me at work (when
OL,12,Fshe found out)!"
